name: World of Warships: Legends — Booster Cache
name_original: World of Warships: Legends — Booster Cache
description:
Head into battle with some extra Premium Account time, Rare Boosters, and Commander XP!

This bundle includes: - 5 days of Premium Account - 5x Rare Ship XP Boosters - 5x Rare Credit Boosters - 5x Rare Commander XP Boosters - 5x Rare Battle Boosters - 37,000 Commander XP

Note: some content, including Boosters, Commander XP, Camouflages, etc., only becomes visible upon reaching a specific account level in the game.
